27b) GET /api/user/search/products
  - Auth: auth:sanctum, role=user
  - Query params:
    - q (required string, max 255)
    - page (optional integer, min 1, default 1)
    - page_size (optional integer, min 1, max 50, default 12)
  - Behavior:
    - Returns full product results matching product title, description, tags, category, condition level, dormitory info, and seller info.
    - Uses full-text indexes (MySQL) and fuzzy matching (SOUNDEX) to handle typos and partial matches.
    - Caches frequent queries for faster responses.
  - Side effect: creates behavioral_events records with event_type "search" for returned products
  - Response 200:
    {
      "message":"Search completed successfully",
